    42 Ã· 2 = 21 â†’ remainder 0

    21 Ã· 2 = 10 â†’ remainder 1

    10 Ã· 2 = 5 â†’ remainder 0

    5 Ã· 2 = 2 â†’ remainder 1

    2 Ã· 2 = 1 â†’ remainder 0

    1 Ã· 2 = 0 â†’ remainder 1

